high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the soap on the counter.
Pick the soap up from the counter.
Go right and stand in front of the double sinks.
Put the soap in the sink to the right, turn the water on and then off and pick the soap up out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the trash can in the corner.
Put the soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap in front of the spray bottle.
Turn right, walk to the end of the counter, turn left.
Put the bar of soap in the sink with the sponge, turn the water on for a few seconds, turn the water off, pick up the soap.
Turn around, walk to the other side of the room, turn right, walk to the other end of the room.
Put the soap in the trash can.
Pick up a bar of soap off of the counter
Move to your right and then face left towards the sinks
Drop the soap in the sink and then run the faucet for a few seconds before picking the soap back up
Turn around and then head all the way to your right
Drop the bar of soap in trash can
anns.task_desc: Wet a bar of soap and throw it in the trash
